# 🔐 Password Reset Backend

A backend API for **user authentication, email verification, and password reset functionality**.  
Built with **Node.js, Express, MongoDB, JWT, Bcrypt, and Nodemailer**.

---

## 🚀 Live API

🔗 [Password Reset Backend (Render Deployment)](https://password-rest-backend-q94i.onrender.com)

---

## 📂 Repository

GitHub Repo: [Password-rest-backend](https://github.com/Sajitha94/Password-rest-backend)

---

## 📌 Features

- ✅ Register user with email only
- ✅ Send **verification code (OTP)** to email (expires in 10 minutes)
- ✅ Verify OTP and allow password setup
- ✅ Secure password storage with **bcrypt**
- ✅ Login with email & password using **JWT authentication**
- ✅ Resend verification token if expired
- ✅ Organized code with `controllers`, `routes`, `utils` structure

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Backend**: Node.js, Express.js
- **Database**: MongoDB + Mongoose
- **Authentication**: JWT (JSON Web Token)
- **Security**: Bcrypt for password hashing
- **Email Service**: Nodemailer with Gmail

---

